The python script pidgin_evt_dump.py plugs itself on dbus and simply dumps
every pidgin messages.
If the output of this script is sent on xmobar, it becomes a simple and
wonderful notification plugin for pidgin :)

xmobar-bottom is the configuration file I use for xmobar

the whole thing is lauched with the command :
pidgin_evt_dump.py | xmobar /home/$USER/.xmonad/xmobar-bottom
